							<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I would argue, post patch, that if you are cash flush, you should have one of each type (stat bump) ring in inventory and buff every stat--at least for a melee class. Certainly I wouldn't blow my entire wad on these, but I run a full buff sequence before raids and tuff fights...and just pop them when I think of them other times.
<br />

<br />
Is it a pain swapping out? Yeah, but with the rings in a bag and the actual fingers on the hotkey bank, its not that much trouble for the value of the buff.<br />_________________<br />Krescendo, 52 Kerran Dirge--Faydark
